.SH NAME
restart-services \- Restart all shared hosting services.
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B restart-services
.RI [ options ]
.SH DESCRIPTION
.B restart-services
attempts to restart configuration-dependent shared hosting services. This
includes nginx, OpenDKIM and PHP-FPM. nginx configuration will be tested before
a reload is attempted.
.SH OPTIONS
